0-06-29 14:05:56','2020-06-29 17:05:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thập Văn Hoan (left) and Phạm Công Giáp with their happy smiles on the Sơn Ca Island. — Photo tuoitre.vn</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HÀ NỘI — Lieutenant Phạm Công Giáp and&nbsp;Thập Văn Hoan are two special soldiers working on the Sơn Ca (Sand Cay) Island.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They are special because they are some of the few ethnic people&nbsp;to step foot on Trường Sa (Spratly) Archipelago of Việt Nam, and because they volunteered to spend their&nbsp;youth in service of the nation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Giáp is&nbsp;a Mường man from the central province of Thanh Hóa and Hoan is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Chăm man from the central-southern province of Ninh Thuận.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Ethnic soldiers proudly serve on Sơn Ca Island','','publish','open','open','','ethnic-soldiers-proudly-serve-on-son-ca-island','','','2020-06-30 11:03:14','2020-06-30 14:03:14','',0,'http://localhost/?p=161',0,'post','',0),(162,1,'2020-06-29 14:05:43','2020-06-29 17:05:43','','','','inherit','open','closed','','vietanme2','','','2020-06-30 11:02:46','2020-06-30 14:02:46','',161,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/vietanme2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(163,1,'2020-06-29 14:05:56','2020-06-29 17:05:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thập Văn Hoan (left) and Phạm Công Giáp with their happy smiles on the Sơn Ca Island. — Photo tuoitre.vn</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HÀ NỘI — Lieutenant Phạm Công Giáp and&nbsp;Thập Văn Hoan are two special soldiers working on the Sơn Ca (Sand Cay) Island.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They are special because they are some of the few ethnic people&nbsp;to step foot on Trường Sa (Spratly) Archipelago of Việt Nam, and because they volunteered to spend their&nbsp;youth in service of the nation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:pa